{"tid":2209944,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"覺得封殺撐中共宣傳係違反言論自由既左膠，你地入一入來，我話你知呢個邏輯謬誤","createTime":"2020-09-20T04:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T06:51:34.000Z","uid":273218,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d682dec58cf37df3d74b1bca33bd85f2bb92b4ff","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:51:19.000Z","msg":"世上有言論自由民主國家<br />\n又有侵犯人權，反言論自由極權國家<br />\n<br />\n幫極權國家宣傳，邏輯上就係助長打壓言論自由，對保障言論自由完全無幫助。<br />\n<br />\n所以封殺甚至立法禁止極權國家宣傳，不單唔係違反言論自由，反而係保障言論自由既根本。<br />\n<br />\n至於點分極權國家，很簡單，中国就係極權國家。<br />\n<br />\n我知道極多人仍拘泥於需要比極權宣傳先係言論自由，唔比佢發言就同共產黨無分別，上面邏輯可以解答晒。"},{"pid":"7d7440925fb168d1d43beb58968db9a91ef234f5","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"立場登撐花木蘭文章擾亂視聽<br />\n<br />\n其實間接幫中共宣傳<br />\n<br />\n如果大家慢慢消化以上邏輯<br />\n<br />\n以後可以名正言順限制中共宣傳"},{"pid":"f328b394814825eed3d6cf12d28b1b7c26ff11e7","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrTABNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrTABNV.jpg&h=32d98d73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82a0ef39814f68f847a8b48d2c9b55643132e106","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7y38WPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7y38WPs.jpg&h=5c9f2859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打緊仗<br />\n撐敵人唔係言論自由"},{"pid":"711cbab492aa0e8657eb3c6a49e4d2a1eba6bd19","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"據聞德國係禁止宣傳納粹<br />\n<br />\n咁撐民主反共既人應該支持禁止宣傳中共"},{"pid":"9fb96843124e6b77cc0a1f9d09476f5f30f93d8c","tid":2209944,"uid":35920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paradox_of_tolerance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FParadox_of_tolerance&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=89bffe1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paradox_of_tolerance</a>"},{"pid":"7384ffb66ffb9753a020a66c2df0cbf79ac03cb7","tid":2209944,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd07909ef78124aab37cc0f38c067fad2fb662f4","tid":2209944,"uid":140492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好對敵人仁慈 人地都唔比你自由民主 言論自由 何必將自己個套強加於人地身上"},{"pid":"ee2054d06ed206d79172ca99852989a977c5c07d","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb96843124e6b77cc0a1f9d09476f5f30f93d8c","tid":2209944,"uid":35920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paradox_of_tolerance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FParadox_of_tolerance&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=89bffe1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paradox_of_tolerance</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"In order to maintain a tolerant society, the society must be intolerant of intolerance"},{"pid":"9a139e28cd7f5613f414ddd123f80a9cb11e8b4e","tid":2209944,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd07909ef78124aab37cc0f38c067fad2fb662f4","tid":2209944,"uid":140492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好對敵人仁慈 人地都唔比你自由民主 言論自由 何必將自己個套強加於人地身上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:49:57.000Z